channel.title: Demolitionx 711
channel.description:
Hey guys I know I started this project before but the person that was hosting the server only cared about money and deleted every single one of my files. I am now restarting with a 667/711 base. I will be starting today on beta mode not completely hosting just to change around and code a bit in the source. This source is not even close to being able to be hosted I have several things I need to edit and am requiring some help on the project. I will have an ongoing update log below, as for now I will post current features of the server.
I currently only want [size=10pt]one[/size] more developer on the team.
Our current release date estimate will be: [size=12pt]UNKOWN[/size]
To apply for the team fill this out please: Name: Age: Time Zone: Time in java (Must be at least 1 year): Experience (PROOF PLEASE):
Our current forums are: NEED APPROVAL
[size=15pt]Update Log[/size] [code] 6/9/12- Added Mystery Boxes With Many Possibilities http://screencast.com/t/b6i2h0323N 6/10/12- Added Flawless Dicing http://screencast.com/t/5L29VhvM 6/11/12- Fixed Armadyl Staff- Fixed Polypore- Fixed TokHaar-Kal Cape- Fixed Economy 6/13/12- New shops 6/17/12- Added Tokens 6/18/12- Added Summoning - Added Full Trade - DFS Is Fixed - Fixed Up Castle Wars 6/19/12- Fixed Auras 100% - Fixed Duel To 100% 6/25/12 - Completely Switched Direction To Pk Server - Added Cool Donor Shop And Pk Shop. - Added 3 Pk Areas. - Added New Money Making System. 6/19/12 - Fixed Un-Equiping - Fixed Barricades At Castle Wars - Fixed Shops From Moving[/code]
[size=12pt]Features From Before My Involvement:[/size] [code] 1>Farming,Mining,Woodcutting,Crafting,Herblore and Rares shop 2>Taken out Starter tutorial so you don't get 99's 3>Added a 500k cash starter 4>Made R.S Webclient look 5>item command only for players whit the privilege not for admins/mods or normal players [/code]
[size=12pt]Features From After My Involvement:[/size] [code] - Added Flawless Dicing http://screencast.com/t/5L29VhvM - Fixed Armadyl Staff - Fixed TokHaar-Kal Cape - Fixed Economy - New shops - Added Tokens WIth System - Added Summoning - Added Full Trade - Added Donor Zone - DFS Is Fixed - Fixed Up Castle Wars - Fixed Auras 100% - Fixed Duel To 100% - Un-Equipping Now Works[/code]
